{"tid":1726544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俾兩日時間政府同藍絲啦","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:12:30.000Z","uid":41873,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b69ccb20c8073d74aa445043c428a13f865133","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"呢兩日由班藍絲活動<br />\n星期一大家繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話唔俾機會你呀政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲有一日半時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩日絕對唔係休息<br />\n希望大家都幫手做文宣<br />\n呢期文宣真係跟唔上"},{"pid":"9fd48237a7fd55e3ef0c8ac5ba046d7e0eafd929","tid":1726544,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b5ffd45d835449ae11a18d075d7fe0e0af81631","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcf23b8b6e096a8318c5f5d4a6a3f79123552aa7","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60d4e37457ae22108ce93d8c2a706c4d4c30e104","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e3aa5708cb9d38f1f7ad0f31009455fb2493d22","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19ef15bccf18d8ae3a0dcd955b30fb8c7b3388f","tid":1726544,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"[重推]全體和理非心聲: 係我哋做得吾夠, 感激前線所有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726402</a>"},{"pid":"61b7ce45c8a295fd804b633133320a067d3a9b1d","tid":1726544,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"f359f6c41fa97c914fcd262ff02e95f87544ac80","tid":1726544,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"要阻礙藍絲活動，一定要勾起佢地自私既心態<br />\n例如，點解我交左稅都要我地去清路障？<br />\n黃絲示威收咁多錢，點解愛港藍絲反而唔值錢？<br />\n路障有二噁英，點解要我去清？<br />\n清路障有幾錢收？<br />\n<br />\n無錢點解要去投票？不如去同仔女行街，訓下覺好過<br />\n投票咁麻煩，無錢點去？<br />\n<br />\n交左稅就應該政府去做，唔應該我地費心<br />\n<br />\n個個都知打人果班收左錢，我無收錢仲要交左稅，點解要我冒住俾人打既風險，交左稅政府唔做野，交來做乜？<br />\n<br />\n幾百蚊清有二噁英既路障，都唔夠我第日睇醫生，仲要可能野到屋企人<br />\n<br />\n班議員每月收咁多錢，竟然叫我地做野？<br />\n<br />\n好心愛國都要食飯架，唔通愛國就唔洗收錢，愛國就賤啲？<br />\n<br />\n搞手之前派成二千去清路障，點解依加得返幾百？個議員又食夾棍？"},{"pid":"fb28be53670132a6e456f789478470a2abfe107d","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd3460df97a86e5d65a0be68034cad0a3a317078","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23d98f2bec69e8c2a30163535d0931fc556876e6","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf1beb33bd66668a6b10a33736ee0fd77c941af4","tid":1726544,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c445f2725eb385e3fddf7567b467feb8a448cc24","tid":1726544,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要點樣先算選舉活動?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726556</a>"},{"pid":"308de67907d60b42cc56ad0be45a93be8e740318","tid":1726544,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":